Interface DependencyInjector.Resolution

  • Enclosing interface:
    DependencyInjector

    public static interface DependencyInjector.Resolution
    Callback methods to resolve the various types of special and regular dependencies.

    Usage

     final ContainerServices services = …;
 final DependencyInjector injector = services.dependencyInjector();
 …
 final DependencyGraph.Node node = injector.resolve(…, new DependencyInjector.Resolution() {
   …
 });
